---
// "O que é Yoga e seus benefícios" — layout editorial centralizado
// (diferente da seção Professora pra evitar repetição visual)
// Imagem em preto e branco com a citação sobreposta
---

<section id="o-que-e-yoga" class="ey-yoga" aria-labelledby="yogaTitle" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/AboutPage">
  <div class="ey-yoga__container">

    <header class="ey-yoga__header">
      <p class="ey-yoga__eyebrow">A Prática</p>
      <h2 class="ey-yoga__title" id="yogaTitle">
        O que é <em>Yoga</em> e seus benefícios
      </h2>
    </header>

    <div class="ey-yoga__intro">
      <p class="ey-yoga__text">
        O <span itemprop="about" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Thing" itemid="https://essenciadoyoga.com.br/#concept-yoga"><span itemprop="name">Yoga</span></span> é uma prática milenar com raízes profundas na espiritualidade, filosofia e cultura da Índia. Seu propósito vai além das posturas físicas: ele busca o equilíbrio entre corpo, mente e espírito.
      </p>
    </div>

    <figure class="ey-yoga__banner">
      <img
        class="ey-yoga__banner-img"
        src="/images/yoga-meditacao-studio.webp"
        alt="Aula de meditação e yoga no studio Essência do Yoga em Sorocaba"
        width="1200"
        height="500"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <blockquote class="ey-yoga__quote">
        <span class="ey-yoga__quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">“</span>
        <p>Cada prática é um convite para respirar com consciência, cultivar presença e reencontrar a sua própria essência.</p>
      </blockquote>
      <figcaption class="ey-yoga__caption">
        <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" />
        <span>Essência do Yoga · Sorocaba/SP</span>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <div class="ey-yoga__outro">
      <p class="ey-yoga__text">
        No <strong>Essência do Yoga</strong>, acreditamos que o Yoga é um caminho de transformação pessoal, acessível a todos, independentemente da idade ou condição física.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="ey-yoga__tags" role="list" aria-label="Pilares da prática">
      <span class="ey-yoga__tag" role="listitem">
        <span class="ey-yoga__tag-num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <span class="ey-yoga__tag-text">Presença</span>
      </span>
      <span class="ey-yoga__tag" role="listitem">
        <span class="ey-yoga__tag-num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <span class="ey-yoga__tag-text">Equilíbrio</span>
      </span>
      <span class="ey-yoga__tag" role="listitem">
        <span class="ey-yoga__tag-num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <span class="ey-yoga__tag-text">Autoconhecimento</span>
      </span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ey-yoga {
    --green: #1D603E;
    --green-deep: #154A30;
    --lime: #BEEBAC;
    --lime-soft: #D6F2CB;
    --lime-pale: #EAF7E4;
    --lilac: #CC6BE6;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --ink: #18241C;
    --ink-soft: #46514A;
    --line: rgba(24, 36, 28, 0.10);

    --font-serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Cormorant Fallback', 'Georgia', serif;
    --font-sans: 'Outfit', 'Outfit Fallback', system-ui, sans-serif;

    --fs-xs: clamp(0.7rem, 0.68rem + 0.12vw, 0.78rem);
    --fs-sm: clamp(0.82rem, 0.8rem + 0.14vw, 0.92rem);
    --fs-base: clamp(0.98rem, 0.92rem + 0.18vw, 1.08rem);
    --fs-3xl: clamp(2.2rem, 1.5rem + 2.4vw, 3.5rem);

    --gutter: clamp(1.5rem, 1rem + 3vw, 4rem);
    --r-md: 16px;
    --r-lg: 24px;
    --r-pill: 999px;

    --ease: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);

    padding: clamp(4rem, 3rem + 4vw, 7rem) 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 80% 10%, rgba(190, 235, 172, 0.18), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 10% 90%, rgba(204, 107, 230, 0.08), transparent 60%),
      var(--white);
    scroll-margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .ey-yoga * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  .ey-yoga__container {
    width: 100% !important;
    max-width: 1100px !important;
    margin: 0 auto !important;
    padding: 0 var(--gutter) !important;
  }

  /* Header */
  .ey-yoga__header {
    text-align: center !important;
    margin-bottom: clamp(1.5rem, 1.2rem + 1vw, 2.25rem) !important;
  }

  .ey-yoga__eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--lilac) !important;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem !important;
  }
  .ey-yoga__eyebrow::before,
  .ey-yoga__eyebrow::after {
    content: "";
    width: 32px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--lilac);
  }

  .ey-yoga__title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--fs-3xl);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .ey-yoga__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  /* Intro / Outro centralizados */
  .ey-yoga__intro,
  .ey-yoga__outro {
    width: 100% !important;
    max-width: 720px !important;
    margin-left: auto !important;
    margin-right: auto !important;
    text-align: center !important;
  }
  .ey-yoga__intro { margin-bottom: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 1.5vw, 3rem) !important; }
  .ey-yoga__outro { margin-top: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 1.5vw, 3rem) !important; margin-bottom: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 1.5vw, 3rem) !important; }

  .ey-yoga__text {
    color: var(--ink-soft) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-sans) !important;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 0.9rem + 0.4vw, 1.15rem) !important;
    line-height: 1.75 !important;
    text-align: center !important;
  }

  /* Banner com imagem em preto e branco + quote sobreposto */
  .ey-yoga__banner {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 21 / 9;
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(15, 26, 18, 0.18);
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .ey-yoga__banner-img {
    width: 100% !important;
    height: 100% !important;
    object-fit: cover !important;
    display: block !important;
    filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(1.02) brightness(0.85);
    transition: filter 600ms var(--ease);
  }

  .ey-yoga__banner::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(15, 26, 18, 0.45) 0%,
      rgba(15, 26, 18, 0.55) 50%,
      rgba(15, 26, 18, 0.75) 100%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* Quote sobreposto */
  .ey-yoga__quote {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
  }

  .ey-yoga__quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 1rem + 1.4vw, 2.1rem);
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--white);
    text-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    text-wrap: balance;
    margin: 0 !important;
  }

  .ey-yoga__quote-mark {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 0.5;
    color: var(--lime);
    opacity: 0.85;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  /* Selo no canto inferior esquerdo */
  .ey-yoga__caption {
    position: absolute;
    left: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.75rem);
    bottom: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.85rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    border-radius: var(--r-pill);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green-deep);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .ey-yoga__caption img { width: 20px !important; height: 20px !important; object-fit: contain !important; }

  /* Tags */
  .ey-yoga__tags {
    display: flex !important;
    flex-wrap: wrap !important;
    justify-content: center !important;
    align-items: center !important;
    gap: clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem) !important;
    text-align: center !important;
  }

  .ey-yoga__tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--r-pill);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    transition: all 350ms var(--ease);
    cursor: default;
  }
  .ey-yoga__tag:hover {
    background: var(--green);
    border-color: var(--green);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(21, 74, 48, 0.18);
  }
  .ey-yoga__tag:hover .ey-yoga__tag-num,
  .ey-yoga__tag:hover .ey-yoga__tag-text {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .ey-yoga__tag-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--lilac);
    transition: color 350ms var(--ease);
  }

  .ey-yoga__tag-text {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--green-deep);
    transition: color 350ms var(--ease);
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ey-yoga { padding: clamp(3rem, 2.5rem + 2vw, 4.5rem) 0; }
    .ey-yoga__banner { aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; }
    .ey-yoga__quote p { font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 4vw, 1.5rem); }
    .ey-yoga__tag { padding: 0.7rem 1.1rem; }
    .ey-yoga__tag-text { font-size: 0.72rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .ey-yoga__tags { flex-direction: column !important; align-items: stretch !important; }
    .ey-yoga__tag { justify-content: center; }
    .ey-yoga__caption { font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ey-yoga__tag { transition: none; }
    .ey-yoga__banner-img { transition: none; }
  }
</style>
